---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Betting Maths Guides"
  description="Plain-English betting maths guides explaining implied probability, overround, bookmaker margin, free bets, matched betting, stake not returned, hedging, dutching, cash out, arbitrage and how bookmakers make money."
>
  <section class="content-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">Betting guides</p>
    <h1>Betting Maths Guides</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Learn the key betting maths concepts behind odds, implied probability, overround, bookmaker margin, free bets, matched betting, stake not returned, hedging, dutching, arbitrage, cash out and back/lay betting.
    </p>

    <div class="callout">
      <strong>Quick guide:</strong> Start with implied probability if you are new to betting maths, then move on to overround, bookmaker margin, free bets, dutching and hedging.
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card article-section">
    <h2>Start here</h2>
    <p>
      These core guides explain the most important concepts behind the calculators on Betting Maths.
    </p>

    <div class="guide-grid">
      <a class="guide-card featured-guide" href="/guides/what-is-implied-probability/">
        <span>Core guide</span>
        <h3>What Is Implied Probability?</h3>
        <p>Learn how betting odds convert into percentage chance and why implied probability matters.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="guide-card featured-guide" href="/guides/bookmaker-margin-explained/">
        <span>Core guide</span>
        <h3>Bookmaker Margin Explained</h3>
        <p>Understand bookmaker margin, overround, book percentage and how market prices are built.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="guide-card featured-guide" href="/guides/what-is-a-free-bet/">
        <span>Core guide</span>
        <h3>What Is a Free Bet?</h3>
        <p>Learn how free bets work, why stake not returned matters, and how offer value is calculated.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card article-section">
    <h2>All betting guides</h2>
    <p>
      Browse all current Betting Maths guides below.
    </p>

    <div class="guide-grid">
      <a class="guide-card" href="/guides/what-is-implied-probability/">
        <span>Odds</span>
        <h3>What Is Implied Probability?</h3>
        <p>Convert odds into percentage chance and understand what a price is suggesting.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="guide-card" href="/guides/bookmaker-margin-explained/">
        <span>Bookmaker margin</span>
        <h3>Bookmaker Margin Explained</h3>
        <p>Learn how bookmaker margin, overround and book percentage are connected.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="guide-card" href="/guides/what-is-overround/">
        <span>Overround</span>
        <h3>What Is Overround in Betting?</h3>
        <p>Understand how betting markets can add up to more than 100%.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="guide-card" href="/guides/how-bookmakers-make-money/">
        <span>Bookmakers</span>
        <h3>How Bookmakers Make Money</h3>
        <p>Learn about overround, odds movement, liability management and weight of money.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="guide-card" href="/guides/can-you-always-beat-the-bookie/">
        <span>Risk</span>
        <h3>Can You Always Beat the Bookie?</h3>
        <p>Learn why guaranteed betting systems are risky and what maths can actually show.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="guide-card" href="/guides/what-is-a-free-bet/">
        <span>Free bets</span>
        <h3>What Is a Free Bet?</h3>
        <p>Understand free bet value, stake not returned, free bet lay stakes and offer terms.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="guide-card" href="/guides/what-is-matched-betting/">
        <span>Matched betting</span>
        <h3>What Is Matched Betting?</h3>
        <p>Learn how qualifying bets, free bets, back bets and lay bets work together.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="guide-card" href="/guides/stake-returned-vs-stake-not-returned/">
        <span>Free bet terms</span>
        <h3>Stake Returned vs Stake Not Returned</h3>
        <p>Learn the difference between cash-style returns and stake-not-returned free bets.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="guide-card" href="/guides/how-to-hedge-a-bet/">
        <span>Hedging</span>
        <h3>How to Hedge a Bet</h3>
        <p>Understand back and lay hedging, lay liability, commission and greening up.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="guide-card" href="/guides/hedging-vs-cash-out/">
        <span>Cash out</span>
        <h3>Hedging vs Cash Out</h3>
        <p>Compare bookmaker cash out offers with manual hedge calculations.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="guide-card" href="/guides/what-is-dutching/">
        <span>Dutching</span>
        <h3>What Is Dutching in Betting?</h3>
        <p>Learn how dutching splits stakes across multiple selections.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="guide-card" href="/guides/dutching-vs-arbitrage/">
        <span>Arbitrage</span>
        <h3>Dutching vs Arbitrage</h3>
        <p>Understand the difference between stake splitting and covering all outcomes.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

