        <h3>Bookmakers and margin</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/guides/how-bookmakers-make-money/">How Bookmakers Make Money</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guides/bookmaker-margin-explained/">Bookmaker Margin Explained</a></li>
