    <h2>Related calculator hub</h2>
    <p>
      If you want to use the tools directly, visit the full calculator hub.
    </p>

    <div class="button-row">
      <a class="button primary" href="/calculators/">Open All Betting Calculators</a>
      <a class="button secondary" href="/glossary/betting-jargon-explained/">Open Betting Glossary</a>
    </div>
